PrecisOrder accepting a "DESIGNATION" duly approved by the FISHER RIVER BAND OF INDIANS whereby the band conditionally surrenders some of the land on FISHER RIVER INDIAN RESERVE No. 44, in the Province of Manitoba, for a term of twenty (20) years, so that it can be leased to third party interests.
